Company Overview of The Rikoon Group, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
The Rikoon Group, LLC is an asset management arm of Sanders Morris Harris Group, Inc. The firm also provides financial counseling services to its clients. It primarily provides its services to individuals and families, typically high net worth individuals. The firm also provides its services to charitable organizations, corporations, and business owners. It manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. It also invests in mutual funds. The firm invests in growth-oriented value stocks to make its equity investments. It employs a fundamental analysis with a bottom-up stock picking a...
The Rikoon Group, LLC is an asset management arm of Sanders Morris Harris Group, Inc. The firm also provides financial counseling services to its clients. It primarily provides its services to individuals and families, typically high net worth individuals. The firm also provides its services to charitable organizations, corporations, and business owners. It manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. It also invests in mutual funds. The firm invests in growth-oriented value stocks to make its equity investments. It employs a fundamental analysis with a bottom-up stock picking approach to make its investments. For its fixed income investments, the firm invests in high-quality government bonds and corporate bonds. It makes socially responsible investments. The firm was formerly known as Rikoon Carret Wealth Management Group, LLC. Rikoon Carret was founded in 1987 and is based in Santa Fe, New Mexico with an additional office in Marshall, North Carolina.
