        Directions              
      





   Directions 


The Rikoon Group is located at 2218 Old Arroyo Chamiso Rd.


From I-25:
Exit at Old Pecos Trail
Take Old Pecos Trail North toward downtown
Turn West on Zia Rd
Continue on W Zia Rd until it dead ends into Old Arroyo Chamiso
Turn right on Old Arroyo Chamiso
We are the first house on the left
A large wall surrounds the property
From St. Francis Dr:
Exit at St. Michael’s Dr.
Head East toward the mountains
Continue East on St. Michael’s for about a mile
Turn South (right) on Arroyo Chamiso Rd.
Take the 3rd left which is Old Arroyo Chamiso Rd
Continue on Old Arroyo Chamiso Rd for about 1/3 of a mile
We are located on the right side of the road
A large wall surrounds the property



